version_description:
Thanks for using Tap & Print!

In this update:
- We have fixed some minor bugs and errors
- Various improvements in functionality and performance

Have problems / ideas? Please contact us at any time!

If you like Tap & Print, please leave a review in App Store.

- Improved duplex printing functionality
- Minor bugs fixed
- Added new localizations

Thanks for using Tap & Print!

- Fixed issue of printing a series of photos on one page

Your feedback is very important.
Please report bugs and problems in the application - we will fix them promptly.

Greetings!

We are glad to present you a new version of Tap & Print!

This is a major update which included:

- Brand New SCANNER Feature with which you can scan any documents and photos using your iPhone or iPad
- Updated main functionality of the application
- Bug fixes and minor improvements

Thanks for being with us all this time!
Your feedback is very important.
Please report bugs and problems in the application - we will fix them promptly.
- Minor functionality improvements according to the user requests

- Some bugs fixes according to the users requests
- Minor functionality improvements
- New localizations

- Improved Scanner functionality
- Minor bug fixes and improvements

Thanks for being with us for almost 3 years!

In this anniversary update 5.0 we have:
- Added over 10 new localizations
- Improved app performance
- Resolved some minor bugs fixes

- Improved app stability and minor bugs fixed
- Better printing settings customization
- Viewing documents became more convenient
- Improved iPadOS appearance
- New stylish icon

- Fixed bug with contacts
- Other improvements

Improvements and bug fixes
- Improved work with documents
- New possibilities for documents processing before printing
